{
"#useparam"
:
true
,
"#name"
:
{
"x gt"
:
null
,
"en"
:
"Manage Gitee work from the command line"
,
"cn"
:
"在命令行管理 Gitee 工作"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Manage Gitee work from the command line"
,
"cn"
:
"在命令行管理 Gitee 工作"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Get Gitee access token: https://gitee.com/profile/personal_access_tokens\n- Interactive env use `x gt init` to initialize configuration. The configure will be saved locally.\n- Run command `x gt --cfg token=<token>` to add access token.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"Gitee 私人令牌获取: https://gitee.com/profile/personal_access_tokens\n- 交互环境中可使用 `x gt init` 进行初始化配置，配置信息将存放于本地保存\n- 亦可运行命令 `x gt --cfg token=<token>` 添加私人令牌\n"
}
]
,
"#keyword"
:
[
"Gitee Cli"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x gt user info"
,
"en"
:
"Get current user information"
,
"cn"
:
"获取当前用户信息"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gt repo ls"
,
"en"
:
"Interactive UI show current user repositories"
,
"cn"
:
"开启交互式表格查看当前用户仓库"
}
]
,
"repo"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"repository management"
,
"cn"
:
"仓库管理"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://gt/data/repo.jso"
}
,
"user"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"user management"
,
"cn"
:
"用户管理"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://gt/data/user.jso"
}
,
"org"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"organization management"
,
"cn"
:
"组织管理"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://gt/data/org/index.jso"
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x gt org ls"
,
"en"
:
"List all organizations for the user"
,
"cn"
:
"罗列当前用户参与的所有组织"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gt org membership add --org <org> --role admin <user>"
,
"cn"
:
"添加 <user> 成员到 <org> 中，并赋予管理员权限"
,
"en"
:
"Add the <user> member to the <org> and grant them admin privileges"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gt org repo ls --type public x-cmd"
,
"en"
:
"List all public repositories under an organization with interactive UI"
,
"cn"
:
"用交互式 UI 列出 x-cmd 组织下所有公开的仓库"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gt org repo create <org_path>/<repo_name>"
,
"en"
:
"Create <repo_name> repo on <org_path> organization"
,
"cn"
:
"在 <org_path> 组织中创建 <repo_name> 仓库"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gt org issue --labels bug --state closed --org x-cmd"
,
"en"
:
"View closed issues with the label \"bug\" in the x-cmd organization"
,
"cn"
:
"查看 x-cmd 组织中标签是 bug, 并且已经关闭的 issue"
}
]
}
,
"enterprise|ent"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"enterprise management"
,
"cn"
:
"企业管理"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://gt/data/enterprise.jso"
}
,
"issue"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"issue management"
,
"cn"
:
"Issue 管理"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://gt/data/issue.jso"
}
,
